Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.66,0:02:04.87,Narrator,(narrator),0,0,0,,{TIME:121663,124875}Maya, along with some other\Nmembers from Tsukikage Theatre,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.87,0:02:09.67,Narrator,(narrator),0,0,0,,{TIME:124875,129671}moved into a small apartment together\Nafter the theatre was demolished.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.67,0:02:13.71,Narrator,(narrator),0,0,0,,{TIME:129671,133717}However, quickly the stress of\Nbalancing school with work
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.71,0:02:16.92,Narrator,(narrator),0,0,0,,{TIME:133717,136928}while hardly being able to practice\Nbegan wearing them down.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.92,0:02:20.43,Narrator,(narrator),0,0,0,,{TIME:136928,140432}Maya's heart was becoming vulnerable.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.35,0:02:27.89,Episode title,[title],0,0,0,,{TIME:141350,147898}{\an5\pos(766,750)\fscy95\blur1\fad(500,500)}—Episode 09—\NMaya's First Movie Appearance
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.90,0:02:39.03,Default,(mixed),0,0,0,,{TIME:156907,159034}– We've got it!\N– You found a place to practice?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.03,0:02:40.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:159034,160702}Yes, we found one!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.70,0:02:43.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:160702,163914}An acquaintance from Rei's job\Nhelped us out.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.41,0:02:45.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:164414,165540}Really? No way!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.54,0:02:49.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:165540,169836}Not only that, it's free!\NWe just have to clean the place up.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.83,0:02:51.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:169836,171546}That's great!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.09,0:03:00.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:178095,180013}Oh, it's a run down church.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.01,0:03:04.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:180013,184601}Yes, but after you clean it up\Nyou can use it all you want
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.60,0:03:07.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:184601,187896}except for during Mass\Non Sundays, Tuesdays and Fridays.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.89,0:03:08.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:187896,188772}Gotcha!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.98,0:03:15.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:193985,195821}Look at you, Maya, you're so into it.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.44,0:03:19.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:196446,199491}I'm so excited to finally start acting again!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.49,0:03:21.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:199491,201491}That's right, it's about time.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.62,0:03:25.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:203620,205372}All right, let's get this done!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.37,0:03:26.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:205372,206373}Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.80,0:03:43.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:220804,223181}I've done exactly what you told me to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.18,0:03:46.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:223181,226518}She looked very happy\Nto have a new place to practice.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.51,0:03:47.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:226518,227518}Good.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.51,0:03:48.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:227518,228687}Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.68,0:03:49.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:228687,229771}Hmm?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.77,0:03:56.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:229771,236403}I thought Tsukikage Theatre's misfortune\Nwas pleasing to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.40,0:03:58.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:236403,238905}Now you have kindly supplied them\Nwith a new practice space,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.90,0:04:00.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:238905,240905}and without even letting them know.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.74,0:04:06.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:243744,246663}I don't want to spoil the golden egg.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.66,0:04:08.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:246663,248081}Is that all there is to it?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.00,0:04:16.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:252001,256506}A skilled secretary should not\Nask pointless questions like these.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.50,0:04:18.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:256506,258091}But, Mr. Masumi,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.09,0:04:20.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:258091,260802}if I am to be your skilled secretary…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.06,0:04:36.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:275066,276818}Teacher…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.61,0:04:40.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:279613,280739}Teacher!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.82,0:04:44.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:282824,284075}Maya!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.07,0:04:46.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:284075,286828}Phew! I was worried\Nwhen I saw you leave like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.16,0:04:49.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:288163,289205}Is the space adequate?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.20,0:04:51.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:289205,291205}Yes, everyone's so happy with it!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.20,0:04:52.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:291205,292167}I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.67,0:05:01.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:299674,301467}Teacher,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.46,0:05:04.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:301467,304054}could you tell me more\Nabout the Crimson Goddess?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.05,0:05:10.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:304054,310644}I wonder if one day I will\Ndeserve a legendary role like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.64,0:05:11.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:310644,311853}You must become a tree.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.85,0:05:12.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:311853,312521}What?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.52,0:05:14.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:312521,314731}Quickly, become a tree.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.73,0:05:17.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:314731,317025}Y-Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.67,0:05:38.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:336670,338505}Maya, does a tree move?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.50,0:05:40.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:338505,340298}Does it scream?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.29,0:05:45.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:340298,345762}You must forget your very humanity\Nif you wish to play a role like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.68,0:05:50.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:346680,350267}Right now, there is not an actress alive\Nworthy of the Crimson Goddess.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.01,0:05:54.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:351017,354104}Maya, you yourself are still\Nvery, very far from worthy.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.06,0:05:57.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:356064,357816}You must continue your practice.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.81,0:06:01.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:357816,361236}You will need to learn and embody\Nhundreds, thousands of roles
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.23,0:06:03.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:361236,363071}before you may approach the Crimson Goddess.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.07,0:06:05.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:363071,365198}Teacher, please tell me.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.19,0:06:07.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:365198,367868}What type of person is the Crimson Goddess?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.86,0:06:11.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:367868,371705}The Crimson Goddess is not a person.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.70,0:06:13.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:371705,373123}She is…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.12,0:06:14.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:373123,374916}A plum tree.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.08,0:06:18.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:378086,378962}A plum…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.00,0:06:21.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:380005,381214}…tree.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.76,0:06:28.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:385760,388346}Ms. Kitajima, did you bring\Nyour textbook fees today?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.88,0:06:30.34,Sign,(sign),0,0,0,,{TIME:387888,390348}Year 3 Group B
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.34,0:06:30.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:388346,390932}I'm sorry, I didn't.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.93,0:06:33.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:390932,393184}Your tardiness is getting to be trouble.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.18,0:06:34.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:393184,394811}As the accountant, I'll be blamed.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.18,0:06:37.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:396187,397105}Damn it…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.10,0:06:38.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:397105,398273}Hey, look!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.27,0:06:40.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:398273,400358}Tabuchi Emi's starring in a movie.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.35,0:06:41.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:400358,401568}Hmm, what kind?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.06,0:06:45.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:403069,405238}Look, they're looking for extras\Nto be her classmates.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.65,0:06:49.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:406656,409618}– Hey, why don't you try out?\N– Let me see!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.61,0:06:50.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:409618,410744}Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.41,0:06:53.74,Thought,,0,0,0,,{TIME:412412,413747}Movies!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.74,0:06:57.95,Thought,,0,0,0,,{TIME:413747,417959}This might be my perfect chance\Nto get a good job.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.46,0:07:02.92,Narrator,(narrator),0,0,0,,{TIME:419461,422923}Maya went out to the audition\Na couple of days later.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.25,0:07:05.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:423256,425216}My gosh, there's so many people.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.21,0:07:06.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:425216,426885}I hope I'll do fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.38,0:07:11.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:429387,431222}So many good-looking people…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.22,0:07:13.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:431222,433266}We're about to start the first auditions.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.26,0:07:14.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:433266,434768}Number 1, please come forward.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.48,0:07:22.23,Narrator,(narrator),0,0,0,,{TIME:438480,442233}The waiting room gradually filled\Nwith uneasiness and nervousness.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.44,0:07:24.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:442442,444569}"I can't believe it… Yoko was doing…"
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.07,0:07:26.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:445070,446488}Next, #87.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.48,0:07:27.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:446488,447238}Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.33,0:07:40.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:458333,460210}Have you memorized the dialogue?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.21,0:07:41.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:460210,461169}Y-Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.46,0:07:43.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:462462,463921}Okay, go ahead.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.30,0:07:52.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:471304,472931}I can't believe it!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.93,0:07:54.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:472931,474849}Yoko was doing just fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.93,0:07:58.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:476935,478353}That's right…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.35,0:08:00.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:478353,480146}To become a tennis player.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.14,0:08:02.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:480146,482482}That was her dream.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.48,0:08:04.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:482482,484109}Why, then…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.73,0:08:05.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:484734,485652}Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.65,0:08:08.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:485652,488488}Why did such a wonderful person\Nhave to die?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.99,0:08:15.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:494995,495828}That will do.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.24,0:08:21.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:499249,501793}The first auditions' results are in.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.79,0:08:25.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:501793,505422}Please proceed for a second audition\Nif your number is called.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.42,0:08:26.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:505422,506339}#16.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.33,0:08:27.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:506339,507298}#27.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.29,0:08:28.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:507298,508299}#31.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.29,0:08:29.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:508299,509174}#60.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.17,0:08:30.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:509174,510093}#80.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.09,0:08:30.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:510093,510969}#87.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.09,0:08:35.34,Narrator,(narrator),0,0,0,,{TIME:512095,515348}The second audition\Nwas also the final audition.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.59,0:08:37.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:515598,517809}You, how are your grades in school?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.80,0:08:39.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:517809,519102}Yes! They're pretty bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.10,0:08:41.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:519102,521146}That's an honest answer.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.14,0:08:43.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:521146,523023}Do you like school?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.02,0:08:44.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:523023,524858}Yes. If there are no classes.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.52,0:08:51.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:528528,531322}Please wait until we announce\Nthe final results.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.07,0:08:59.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:532073,539289}Let's go with applicants\N#16, #27, #31, #60 and #80.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.28,0:09:02.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:539289,542917}No, I say we keep #87.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.91,0:09:04.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:542917,544334}But…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.33,0:09:08.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:544334,548548}She's not especially beautiful,\Nand her personality is nothing special.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.54,0:09:12.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:548548,552844}For some reason though, when she read\Nthe short dialogue, she caught my heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.84,0:09:15.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:552844,555472}"Some reason" isn't good enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.27,0:09:23.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:562270,563605}Thank you for waiting.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.60,0:09:27.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:563605,567275}We've chosen five classmates for Tabuchi Emi.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.27,0:09:28.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:567275,568276}#16.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.27,0:09:29.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:568276,569401}#27.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.40,0:09:30.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:569401,570487}#31.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.48,0:09:31.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:570487,571446}#60.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.44,0:09:32.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:571446,572363}#80.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.36,0:09:33.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:572363,573490}That's all.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.07,0:09:40.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:579079,580080}Hey, you!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.08,0:09:41.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:580080,581664}#87, excuse me!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.08,0:09:45.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:585085,585752}Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.75,0:09:47.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:585752,587337}Me? In the movie?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.33,0:09:49.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:587337,589380}Yes, only a small part though.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.38,0:09:51.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:589380,591466}I'll still be in the movie, then?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.46,0:09:52.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:591466,592382}Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.38,0:09:54.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:592382,594928}I'm Toda, chief assistant director.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.92,0:09:56.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:594928,596137}So, can you do it?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.13,0:09:57.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:596137,597013}Absolutely!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.01,0:09:58.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:597013,598515}Even a pedestrian is fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.76,0:10:03.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:601768,603684}Wow, good job!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.68,0:10:04.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:603684,604604}Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.60,0:10:08.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:604604,608608}I got a small role as a patient\Nwhere Tabuchi Emi is hospitalized.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.60,0:10:10.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:608608,610608}Only a small role, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.73,0:10:15.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:611736,615824}A girl with a paralyzed left leg…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.82,0:10:17.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:615824,617742}You even have two lines.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.74,0:10:18.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:617742,618868}That's great.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.86,0:10:19.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:618868,619619}Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.61,0:10:21.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:619619,621454}I want to try anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.54,0:10:29.75,Thought,,0,0,0,,{TIME:626543,629754}Even though this is a small role,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.75,0:10:31.71,Thought,,0,0,0,,{TIME:629754,631714}it could be a useful lesson for my future.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.96,0:10:36.34,Retrospective,,0,0,0,,{TIME:632966,636343}You will need to learn to embody\Nhundreds, thousands of roles
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.34,0:10:38.38,Retrospective,,0,0,0,,{TIME:636343,638388}before you may approach the Crimson Goddess.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.38,0:10:39.84,Thought,,0,0,0,,{TIME:638388,639848}It doesn't matter what the role is.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.84,0:10:41.01,Thought,,0,0,0,,{TIME:639848,641015}I will do my very best.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.32,0:11:02.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:661327,662412}Teacher!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.13,0:11:15.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:672130,675717}Maya! You cannot support yourself\Non a paralyzed leg!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.92,0:11:20.38,Thought,,0,0,0,,{TIME:676926,680388}I used my leg without even thinking.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.38,0:11:22.68,Thought,,0,0,0,,{TIME:680388,682682}A paralyzed leg couldn't have held me up.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.68,0:11:26.01,Thought,,0,0,0,,{TIME:682682,686019}Mr. Tsukikage pushed me to teach me that!
Comment: 0,0:11:30.98,0:11:30.98,Default,[chapter],0,0,0,,{TIME:690982,690982}Eyecatch
Comment: 0,0:11:34.77,0:11:34.77,Default,[chapter],0,0,0,,{TIME:694776,694776}#Eyecatch
Comment: 0,0:11:37.78,0:11:37.78,Default,[chapter],0,0,0,,{TIME:697780,697780}Part B
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.33,0:11:51.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:709334,711961}Oh, that's Ms. Tabuchi Emi.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.46,0:11:56.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:714464,716507}Point it upward a little.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.50,0:11:58.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:716507,718301}I got it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.96,0:12:01.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:718968,721512}That's not good at all, Emi.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.51,0:12:03.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:721512,723473}I don't know what you mean…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.47,0:12:05.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:723473,725767}You sound like you're reading a book.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.76,0:12:09.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:725767,729812}I've never acted before, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.81,0:12:13.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:729812,733399}Besides, I had to tape a show this morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.39,0:12:16.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:733399,736444}I'm too tired to put on a good act.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.44,0:12:19.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:736444,739530}Sorry, but can we get a little break?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.53,0:12:21.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:739530,741824}Okay, ten minute break!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.82,0:12:23.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:741824,743910}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.28,0:12:27.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:745286,747455}Even more tabloid interviews?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.75,0:12:33.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:750750,753086}Emi, how's your first acting job?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.08,0:12:36.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:753086,756256}Well, I think acting is fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.25,0:12:38.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:756256,758256}Would you like to become\Nan actress in the future?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.09,0:12:41.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:759092,761469}Well, if there are any good movies.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.46,0:12:43.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:761469,763513}Just imagine it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.76,0:12:47.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:766766,767517}Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.51,0:12:49.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:767517,769602}Let's shoot for the hospital scene.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.60,0:12:51.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:769602,771312}Please stand by.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.31,0:12:52.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:771312,772188}Emi!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.14,0:12:56.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:774147,776442}Sorry, but it's time for her next appointment.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.44,0:12:58.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:776442,778278}We have a TV show to make.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.27,0:12:58.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:778278,778987}See ya!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.98,0:12:59.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:778987,779779}Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.77,0:13:01.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:779779,781698}Great work! See you tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.44,0:13:05.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:782448,785867}What does she think she's here for?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.86,0:13:08.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:785867,788246}We're making a movie here.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.24,0:13:08.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:788246,788913}Geez.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.91,0:13:09.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:788913,789914}No kidding.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.91,0:13:12.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:789914,792542}Our schedule is already messed up,\Nall because of her.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.00,0:13:18.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:797005,798673}I'm…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.13,0:13:22.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:800133,802676}really anemic…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.38,0:13:25.88,Default,(mixed),0,0,0,,{TIME:803386,805888}– Uhm…\N– No good!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.88,0:13:28.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:805888,808349}You haven't even memorized any of it!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.34,0:13:31.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:808349,811185}Sorry about that, but she's been busy.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.18,0:13:35.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:811185,815189}Besides, she's a singer,\Nnot an actress.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.18,0:13:37.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:815189,817233}I don't care if she's a singer.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.23,0:13:39.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:817233,819233}She needs to be a professional.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.23,0:13:44.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:819233,824282}People will be paying to see this movie!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.70,0:13:52.66,Thought,,0,0,0,,{TIME:829704,832665}I keep practicing, but it's only imitation.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.66,0:13:54.62,Thought,,0,0,0,,{TIME:832665,834625}I just can't understand the pain.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.62,0:13:57.71,Thought,,0,0,0,,{TIME:834625,837712}The inconvenience,\Nthe anguish of being paralyzed.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.71,0:13:58.62,Thought,,0,0,0,,{TIME:837712,838628}How?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.26,0:14:05.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:844260,845011}Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.01,0:14:07.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:845011,847221}We'll move on to the hospital lobby scene.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.22,0:14:09.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:847221,849182}Emi, please come and sit here.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.18,0:14:10.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:849182,850683}Hold on just a sec.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.60,0:14:14.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:852602,854854}Okay, everyone, get in place.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.85,0:14:16.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:854854,856356}Look at her.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.31,0:14:22.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:860318,862862}What… are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.86,0:14:27.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:862862,867200}I couldn't feel like I was paralyzed,\Nso I decided to do this during rehearsals.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.12,0:14:36.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:875124,876125}Emi!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.37,0:14:39.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:877377,879587}Hurry up!\NThe director's been waiting.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.58,0:14:41.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:879587,881214}Sorry for being late.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.59,0:14:45.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:883591,885093}What is she doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.09,0:14:47.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:885093,887470}Well, she's been doing that for two hours.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.47,0:14:49.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:887470,889931}She just climbs and descends the stairs like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.93,0:14:51.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:889931,891140}Two hours?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.14,0:14:53.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:891140,893017}Is that girl stupid?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.01,0:14:55.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:893017,895103}She's only got some tiny role.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.60,0:14:58.64,Thought,,0,0,0,,{TIME:897605,898647}I'm getting it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.64,0:15:02.56,Thought,,0,0,0,,{TIME:898647,902568}The pain my character feels\Nis starting to feel real.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.56,0:15:06.82,Thought,,0,0,0,,{TIME:902568,906823}I'm understanding this girl's\Nstruggle to live the best she can.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.07,0:15:11.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:909075,911536}Scene 34, take 1.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.53,0:15:12.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:911536,912328}Action!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.97,0:15:32.43,Thought,,0,0,0,,{TIME:929971,932432}This is what her training was all for.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.43,0:15:34.26,Thought,,0,0,0,,{TIME:932432,934267}She made her left leg go numb.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.76,0:15:39.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:936769,939230}The way she walks…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.23,0:15:42.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:939230,942650}It's almost like she's really paralyzed.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.33,0:16:02.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:961335,962627}I've come to watch.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.62,0:16:04.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:962627,964672}Oh, Mr. Tanabe.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.46,0:16:12.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:970469,972054}That girl…!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.05,0:16:14.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:972054,974474}Oh, she didn't pass\Nthe audition for Emi's classmates.,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.47,0:16:18.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:974474,978186}but we decided to use her as an extra.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.18,0:16:19.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:978186,979937}Do you guys have any eyes?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.93,0:16:20.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:979937,980646}Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.64,0:16:24.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:980646,984942}She's the girl who competed against\NHimekawa Ayumi at the National Acting Contest.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.94,0:16:29.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:984942,989197}The audience loved her,\Nshe won the popular vote.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.19,0:16:32.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:989197,992200}Himekawa Ayumi, the acting genius?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.47,0:16:55.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1014472,1015598}What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.59,0:16:58.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1015598,1018226}Tabuchi Emi can't even move.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.06,0:17:04.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1023064,1024232}Close up!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.23,0:17:04.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1024232,1024774}Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.77,0:17:05.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1024774,1025816}What are you doing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.81,0:17:07.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1025816,1027108}Not on Tabuchi Emi!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.10,0:17:08.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1027108,1028194}On that girl!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.19,0:17:10.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1028194,1030112}Close up on her at once!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.07,0:17:13.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1032073,1033449}I'll do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.90,0:17:54.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1072905,1074532}Here, you dropped this.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.53,0:17:55.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1074532,1075575}Cut!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.46,0:18:07.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1086460,1087753}Welcome home!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.83,0:18:11.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1088838,1091048}Oh, you're still up.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.04,0:18:12.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1091048,1092508}You haven't finished studying?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.50,0:18:15.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1092508,1095386}Yes, I've felt so hungry for knowledge.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.38,0:18:18.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1095386,1098055}I want to go see a play in England or New York,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.05,0:18:20.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1098055,1100683}I need to become more wordly.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.51,0:18:22.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1101517,1102602}Hey, Dad.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.60,0:18:25.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1102602,1105104}May I join you in England\Nwhen you shoot there?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.10,0:18:25.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1105104,1105812}Please.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.81,0:18:27.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1106814,1107773}Utako.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.77,0:18:30.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1107773,1110318}You've got a strong rival in front of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.36,0:18:36.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1112360,1116949}If Ayumi can become a better actress\Nthan I am, I will be very proud.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.94,0:18:38.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1116949,1118242}Then, Mom…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.24,0:18:41.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1118242,1121370}You wouldn't mind if some day\NI starred in "The Crimson Goddess"?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.28,0:18:45.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1123289,1125833}If you become a great enough actress.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.83,0:18:47.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1125833,1127710}You still have so much learning to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.58,0:18:51.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1129587,1131797}That role is famous for being difficult.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.79,0:18:55.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1131797,1135593}I remember Miss Tsukikage saying to me,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.59,0:18:57.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1135593,1137637}"The Crimson Goddess is a plum tree.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.63,0:19:00.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1137637,1140139}You have to abandon\Nevery bit of your humanity."
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.09,0:19:03.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1141098,1143726}I know that you are very talented.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.72,0:19:07.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1143726,1147146}But sometimes talent is not enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.14,0:19:09.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1147146,1149774}You need experience.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.77,0:19:13.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1149774,1153527}In my twenty years as an actress,\NI have played so many roles.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.36,0:19:18.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1156364,1158866}Now, you should go to bed.\NIt's gotten quite late.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.61,0:19:21.16,Thought,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1159617,1161160}I understand, Mom.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.16,0:19:24.33,Thought,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1161160,1164330}I have to be able to play any role.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.54,0:19:33.83,Sign,(sign),0,0,0,,{TIME:1168542,1173839}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.08,0:19:35.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1172088,1175174}All right, I wonder how Maya did
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.17,0:19:37.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1175174,1177593}I-It's only a small role.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.59,0:19:41.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1177593,1181555}I probably won't get more than a second,\Nand it might just be my back.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.55,0:19:42.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1181555,1182890}Okay, okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.76,0:19:47.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1186769,1187812}Look, that's Maya!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.71,0:20:13.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1211711,1213462}Whoa…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.46,0:20:14.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1213462,1214213}A close-up.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.04,0:20:17.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1215047,1217466}Full screen.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.13,0:20:19.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1218134,1219760}For an unknown actress.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.76,0:20:20.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1219760,1220928}What a surprise!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.56,0:20:30.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1228561,1230562}Here, you dropped this.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.28,0:20:43.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1241282,1243325}Hello, I came to pick you up.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.91,0:20:49.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1247913,1249290}How did you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.29,0:20:53.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1249290,1253461}I'm your secretary, Mr. Masumi.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.84,0:21:02.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1257840,1262928}You must have really looked forward\Nto this movie to drop your entire schedule.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.39,0:21:09.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1267391,1269560}Emi, great job.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.56,0:21:11.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1269560,1271604}Any plans for the next movie?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.60,0:21:14.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1271604,1274273}Tell us, what is your next project?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.15,0:21:17.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1276150,1277651}I don't know yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.65,0:21:22.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1277651,1282865}But if I get a chance soon,\NI'm planning to study acting.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.78,0:21:29.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1287787,1289914}Cheers!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.91,0:21:33.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1289914,1293626}How nice that you're treating us\Nwith your first paycheck.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.62,0:21:36.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1293626,1296003}Are you okay buying cake and stuff?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.00,0:21:38.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1296003,1298005}Your little paycheck will be gone.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.00,0:21:38.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1298005,1298798}I'm fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.79,0:21:40.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1298798,1300591}I have a little bit left.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.59,0:21:43.17,Thought,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1300591,1303177}I can pay for my books now.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.17,0:21:45.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1303177,1305387}All right, cheers again.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.38,0:21:46.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1305387,1306305}Cheers!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.97,0:21:47.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1306972,1307807}What?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.80,0:21:51.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1307807,1311185}I would like to take the animal tamer's role.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.80,0:21:52.26,Sign,(sign),0,0,0,,{TIME:1307807,1312268}Beauty and the Beast
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.18,0:21:52.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1311185,1312269}It's not assigned yet, correct?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.26,0:21:56.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1312269,1316607}Well, no one wanted to play this role.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.60,0:22:00.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1316607,1320611}Besides, this "Beauty and the Beast"\Nisn't for a big theater.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.60,0:22:04.03,Sign,(sign),0,0,0,,{TIME:1316607,1324031}Beauty and the Beast
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.61,0:22:02.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1320611,1322321}It's a charity play for an orphanage.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.32,0:22:04.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1322321,1324031}Fine. I'll take it.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.32,0:22:07.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1324323,1327827}Someone like you can't play such a small role.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.82,0:22:08.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1327827,1328702}She's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.70,0:22:10.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1328702,1330162}You should play the main role!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.16,0:22:10.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1330162,1330913}No.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.91,0:22:12.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1330913,1332623}This is the role I want.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.62,0:22:15.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1332623,1335417}I want to challenge myself\Nand expand my image.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.41,0:22:18.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1335417,1338379}It doesn't matter if the role is big or small.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.25,0:22:20.29,Thought,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1339255,1340297}Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.29,0:22:22.84,Thought,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1340297,1342842}And one day I will play\Nthe Crimson Goddess.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.48,0:22:42.02,Thought,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1360484,1362027}Someday…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.02,0:22:44.44,Thought,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1362027,1364446}Someday, I'll star in\N"The Crimson Goddess".
