Dialogue: 0,0:24:24.42,0:24:28.75,Narrator,(narrator),0,0,0,,{TIME:1464421,1468759}Maya's burning passion for theatre\Ncalls her to the stage,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:28.75,0:24:31.01,Narrator,(narrator),0,0,0,,{TIME:1468759,1471011}but every step of the way she is refused.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:31.01,0:24:36.68,Narrator,(narrator),0,0,0,,{TIME:1471011,1476684}Meanwhile her rival, Ayumi, prepares to play\Nthe animal tamer in "Beauty and the Beast".
